{
  "text": "The remainder of the sample was fixed in 4% gluteraldehyde for TEM examination. This was processed through to resin by standard techniques. [CITATION_1] Ultrathin sections were cut at 70 nm, collected on 200 mesh thin bar copper grids, stained in 1% uranyl acetate and counterstained in Reynold's lead phosphate before assessment by TEM in a blind fashion.",
